Sun Sentinel Article about The Adventures of Charlie Pierce<br/><br/>&lt;blockquote&gt;It’s very well-written,” says Liz Perlman, Palm Beach County schools district director for elementary curriculum, “and the timing was great. We study Florida in fourth grade, and this is the year of the Everglades. To use this book to talk about Florida history and ecology is awesome.&lt;/blockquote&gt;
